Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.98,Italics Top,announcement,0000,0000,0000,,The train about to arrive on track...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:09.13,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me straight, Nukumizu.\N I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:15.66,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\fscx90\fs12\fay-0.05\fax0.06\bord0\shad0\blur0.5\c&H28321C&\frx0\fry354\pos(493.334,52)}Toyohashi's Famous
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:15.66,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\fs22\fscx80\fscy110\bord0\fay-0.006\shad0\blur0.5\frz2.137\frx0\fry356\c&H241A55&\pos(494,96)}Yamasa\NChikuwa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:13.95,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I can accept Chihaya finding \Nsomeone new if it's you—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.65,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wait, wait, wait! \NThat's not what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.62,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\fs42\fscx80\fscy110\bord0\fay-0.006\shad0\blur0.5\frz2.137\frx0\fry356\c&H241A55&\pos(570,68.667)}Yamasa\NChikuwa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:18.62,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Then why were you guys together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:26.43,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you have a \Nlittle explaining to do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:28.65,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.76,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What were you and Yakishio doing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.28,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,You two were walking by \Nthe station a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.37,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! We weren't \Ndoing anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:40.39,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was just because...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:46.85,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I was asking Lemon for relationship advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.56,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Relationship advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:58.83,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I've never gone out with a girl before,\N and I wanted some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.92,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you ask Yakishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:07.39,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Well, Lemon's really popular. \NShe probably understands how girls feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.97,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:13.44,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,What were you and Chihaya doing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.43,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We were... well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:20.39,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I was, you know, asking her \Nfor relationship advice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:22.32,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Relationship advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:27.50,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,But, dude, don't you have female friends in \Nthe lit club? Why'd you need to ask Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:28.23,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:33.45,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! The girl you like \Nmust be in the literature club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:36.61,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.24,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Is it Lemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.66,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't. You can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:43.19,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Well, in that case,\N just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:44.16,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Leave what to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:49.67,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,I know everyone says I'm dense and stuff,\N but this might just clear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.92,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Give her a call and let's \Nall go hang out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.24,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for dragging you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.15,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally fine. I was free anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:38.23,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad Asagumo-san \Nfound out he wasn't cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.97,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.59,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:47.24,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Nukumizu-san and Yanami-san.\NLet's enjoy ourselves today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:54.42,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,The only one here who doesn't \Nrealize today is a setup is Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:58.49,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,And Yakishio thinks we did it\N just to hang out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.80,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:03.92,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:08.51,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation. Five high \Nschool students. Boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.87,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You see what I'm saying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.56,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.44,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,We're totally in the prime \Nof our youth. We're glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:19.32,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Check out the effort I put into my outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.32,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\b1\fax-0.07\blur0.3\fscx85\fs35\frz5.273\frx19\c&H888980&\pos(319.333,97.333)}City of Toyohashi Underground Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.74,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,So why the hell are we at \Nan underground museum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.82,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,It even has "underground" in the name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:29.33,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I know boys might find stuff \Nlike this fun, but what about the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.87,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.70,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, look at this! \NWhat magnificent pieces of mica!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.92,Default,Chihaya,0000,0000,0000,,How many capacitors do you think \Nthey could make with just one of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.99,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's a minecart! A minecart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.78,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Are we allowed to ride it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.47,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Am I in the minority here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.76,Default,kids,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:50.63,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Was it your idea to \Ncome here today, Nuk-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:55.56,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, no. Ayano and I chatted \Nand decided on this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:59.52,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But it was his idea to get everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.24,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. So it was Mitsuki's idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.58,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,When did you become\Nsuch good friends with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.78,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it just sort of happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.08,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.00,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.58,Default,Ayano,0000,0000,0000,,So what's your favorite \Ntype of capacitor, Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.68,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:24.04,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good. I don't want to spoil \NMitsuki and Chihaya's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.72,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to have plenty \Nof time together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.55,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:32.19,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Are you weirdly worried about \Nmy feelings or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:41.57,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good. I'm, like, their biggest cheerleader.\N Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.33,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.38,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good with the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:56.10,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're always acting silly and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.94,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,but at times like this,\Nyou seem really mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:03.21,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. Took you long enough to notice.
